<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/composedof> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                     rdfs:subPropertyOf owl:topObjectProperty .


###  https://w3id.org/pmd/co/input
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/input> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty .


###  https://w3id.org/pmd/co/output
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/output> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty .


